Diagnosed package naming mismatch and workspace dependency configuration issues
That import string was my guess — it has to match the actual package name yarn new gave your plugin, and yours is almost certainly different. Two things to check, in order.

First, find the real name. Open plugins/production-requests-backend/package.json and look at the "name" field:

bash
