The HTTP client (api/ProductionRequestsApi.ts)
The frontend shouldn't hardcode localhost:7007 — Backstage's discoveryApi resolves a plugin's base URL for you, and fetchApi is the fetch wrapper that attaches auth when we add it later. The client wraps the three endpoints.

