The problem is contrast: your fields sit on the InfoCard's paper background with transparent fills, so they visually disappear into the card. The professional look comes from a two-tone setup — a slightly tinted panel with crisp white fields sitting on top of it, plus a proper form footer. Here's the reworked component:

