1. The merger's name is in the wrong place. GitLab puts the user who triggered the event at the top of the payload, not inside object_attributes:

ts
// you have:
actor: object_attributes?.user?.name ?? 'gitlab-webhook',
// should be:
actor: req.body.user?.name ?? req.body.user?.username ?? 'gitlab-webhook',
