No Origin header → it's same-origin, CORS is irrelevant, your problem is elsewhere (the LDAP 404 or baseUrl). Stop touching CORS.
An Origin header with a real value → put that exact value in the origin: array (string or array form above).
Origin: null → it's an AWB/proxy wrapping issue, fix it there.
