Backend config (CORS, database, LDAP, listen port) — runtime, read from the YAML in the container at startup. Not baked by the build. Change YAML + restart.

Frontend config (app.baseUrl, backend.baseUrl) — build-time, compiled into the JS. Must pass the production config to the build, or the browser gets dev URLs.

